snippet.title: Tournament of Legends Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Become a legend in epic weapon and magic duels against the biggest fighters of world mythology.

Enter powerful battles with a rich assortment of blade weapons and tons of magical attacks. No other Wii™ weapon fighting game offers this much variety and challenge. Tournament of Legends is set to release in May 2010 exclusively for Wii.
